How to add new functional tests?

  1. Group the tests by route;

  2. Name the test files following the rule:
    <HTTP_METHOD>-<ROUTE_PATH_SEPARATED_BY_->-tests.js

    Examples:
      post-users-tests.js
      get-users-{userId}-tests.js

  3. Edit the file runner.js to define what tests must be ran:
    - The tests always run in serie


Executing the tests

  npm run test:functional
  npm run test:functional:debug
